    "descriptionHtml": "<h2>Thirtyfifth</h2>\n<p>A bit late given this is going up in the last hour of Monday but it still counts, right? Right. Left out a lot of really great music off this mix. Maybe someday I should do a Monday Music Mix: Rejects edition. Soon.</p>\n<p><strong>Monday Music Mix: 35</strong></p>\n<p><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"400\" data-orig-width=\"400\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/555f756c6ac8f15c99699f1aff623d66/a9ae05f1087cd924-30/s540x810/5460a8cf8f174fb3e930b5f4a08734ed1a200fbd.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"400\" data-orig-width=\"400\"/></figure></p>\n\n<p>Album art featuring work by <a href=\"http://www.andrewsalgado.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Andrew Salgado</a></p>\n<p>Tracklist:</p>\n<ol><li>Chromeo - Over Your Shoulder</li>\n<li>White Denim - Pretty Green</li>\n<li>Young Galaxy - Sea Drug</li>\n<li>Wolf Alice - Blush</li>\n<li>Meg Myers - Desire</li>\n<li>Phantogram - Black Out Days</li>\n<li>Society - 14 Hours</li>\n<li>Braids - Hossak</li>\n<li>Anna Lunoe - Breathe</li>\n<li>Jungle - The Heat</li>\n<li><strong>Yamantaka // Sonic Titan - One</strong></li>\n<li>Shy Girls - Still Not Falling</li>\n<li><strong>The Wyld - Odyssey</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Goldroom - Embrace</strong></li>\n<li>Laura Welsh - Undiscovered</li>\n</ol><p>* Tracks in bold indicate my favourites</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://mega.co.nz/#!wRoTFI4b!LoNgkTb7YUmss7dwmS53NxZrMgcFqeC6jvmbaICvB4Y\" target=\"_blank\">Download album</a></p>"
